def module anchor-macro
def desc "press z and place an anchor and explode it fast (mdae by megan)"
on key_press Z if playing wait 0.001 then switch #anchor then input right then wait_random 0.05 0.1 switch #glowstone then input right then wait_random 0.05 0.1 then switch #totem then wait_random 0.05 0.1 then input right